'''Laami''' ({{lang-en|Road surface iyo pavement}}) waa aalad la dulsaaro meelo ka mid ah oogada dhulka, si looga sameeyo [[wado]] siman oo [[dad]]ka ama [[gaadiid]]ku ku dulsocon karaan si sahal ah. Sida ugu badan laamiga waxaa laga sameeyaa quruurax (dhagaxaan la jajabshey), sibidh, dhoobo iyo [[gaamur]] la iskuqasay. 
Meelaha qaar laamiyada waxaa laga sameeyaa sibid iyo jaajuur la iskudhex laaqay.
